        <title>Save Social Security First Act of 2003</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to restore the applicability of the estate tax to estates over $3,000,000, to restore the 50-percent maximum rate, and to deposit revenues from the estate tax into Social Security Trust Funds.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
        <billTextVersionCode>IH</billTextVersionCode>
